txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Heavy carapaces from the insects in the lands west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger, Astiul, at the outpost on the shores of Lake Evendim.
'I will see that these are given to those who can put them to good use.'
'When we run low on supplies, the carapaces of the insects to the west might be useful to patch boats or other things. If you come by any, bring them here.'
Wardens of Ann√∫minas Task: Heavy Carapaces
Tinnudir, a Ranger-outpost on the eastern shore of Lake Evendim, is home to the Rangers of Evendim. There, at the outpost, a Ranger named Astiul awaits the return of heavy carapaces.
Deliver the heavy carapaces to Astiul at the Ranger-outpost of Tinnudir
You have been tasked with collecting heavy carapaces from the insects to the west of Tinnudir. You are to deliver the items to the Ranger Astiul within the lakeside outpost.
Wanted: Heavy carapaces from the insects in the lands west of the Ranger-outpost at Tinnudir.
